@page "/"
@rendermode InteractiveServer

<h2>Welcome</h2>
<p>
    This sample wires Trax + SignalR end-to-end. The scheduler queues a
    <code>PingTrain</code> every 10 seconds and an in-process worker executes it.
    Every lifecycle event flows through the SignalR sink to connected browsers.
</p>
